Fully furnished 1 bedroom condo on the third floor with amazing views in Dupont on the border of Kalorama. This property is accessed by walking up two flights of stairs and no elevator. It features an updated kitchen and bathroom, an in-unit washer/dryer, a&nbsp;full sized sofa, working fireplace, hardwood floors, high ceilings, a 180 degree view from the turret window and a queen sized bed in the bedroom.&nbsp;
Located just three blocks to the Dupont Circle Metro Station (red line), 15-20 minute walk to Adams Morgan, U Street, and Georgetown, the property is surrounded by coffee shops, fantastic restaurants, upscale boutique shops, amenities and more! &nbsp;Walk Score: 96 (Walkers Paradise), Transit Score: 81, Bike Score: 84.&nbsp;
