This fully furnished 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 3 level home is in a great location just two blocks from the heart of Friendship Heights. This home features hardwood floors,&nbsp;a well-appointed living room with a wood burning fireplace, and a remodeled open floor plan kitchen/dining room with breakfast bar. The top floor also includes an additional room that can be used as an office, playroom or extra bedroom. The house has&nbsp;central air, an on-site Washer and Dryer, a front porch and a fully-fenced landscaped back yard complete with a patio.&nbsp;
Easy access to Mazza Gallerie and all of its great shops, restaurants, theater, Whole Foods, Cheesecake Factory, Starbucks, and more. There are numerous parks within walking distance. The Friendship Heights Metro Station (Red Line) is a short 4 minute walk away and bus lines across the street and nearby get you everywhere you want to go! The area has many private and public schools, including Janney Elementary School, Deal Middle, and Wilson High School.&nbsp;&nbsp; Excellent private preschools are also&nbsp;nearby. Walk score gives this location a 90, a &ldquo;walker&rsquo;s paradise.&rdquo;&nbsp;
